				</div>
				<div class="proof-item">
					<div class="proof-icon">üõ°Ô∏è</div>
					<h3>Fully Licensed & Insured</h3>
					<p>Complete protection with comprehensive liability, bonding, and workers' compensation coverage.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="proof-item">
					<div class="proof-icon">‚≠ê</div>
